headline: Market Sell-Off: 1 Growth Stock Down 25% to Buy Right Now
summary: With the recent market sell-off, a number of growth stocks have fallen from their highs.  One such stock that could give investors' portfolios a jolt is Dutch Bros (NYSE: BROS).  The coffeehouse operator has a number of potential growth drivers over the next few years that should help power its stock moving forward.
